<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١١٦- <span class="c1">"المُكرِمُ"</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">دليله:</span> قوله تعالى: <span class="c3">{وَلَقَدْ كَرَّمْنَا بَنِي آدَمَ وَحَمَلْنَاهُمْ فِي الْبَرِّ وَالْبَحْرِ}</span> . <span class="c2">(الإسراء: من الآية٧٠)</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">من ذكره:</span> ذكره الشرباصي.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١١٧- <span class="c1">"الممتَحِن"</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">دليله:</span> قوله تعالى: <span class="c3">{أُولَئِكَ الَّذِينَ امْتَحَنَ اللَّهُ قُلُوبَهُمْ لِلتَّقْوَى}</span> . <span class="c2">(الحجرات: من الآية٣)</span> .<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">من ذكره:</span> ١- ابن العربي. ٢- القرطبي. ٣- الشرباصي.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١٨- <span class="c1">"المُمِدُّ"</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">دليله:</span> قوله تعالى: <span class="c3">{وَأَمْدَدْنَاكُمْ بِأَمْوَالٍ وَبَنِينَ}</span> . <span class="c2">(الإسراء: من الآية٦)</span> .<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">من ذكره:</span> ذكر في جمع الشرباصي.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١١٩- <span class="c1">"المُمْلي"</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">دليله:</span> قوله تعالى: <span class="c3">{وَأُمْلِي لَهُمْ إِنَّ كَيْدِي مَتِينٌ}</span> . <span class="c2">(لأعراف:١٨٣)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">من ذكره:</span> ذكره الشرباصي.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١٢٠-<span class="c1">"المُمهِلُ"</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">دليله:</span> قوله تعالى: <span class="c3">{فَمَهِّلِ الْكَافِرِينَ أَمْهِلْهُمْ رُوَيْداً}</span> . <span class="c2">(الطارق:١٧)</span> .<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">من ذكره:</span> ذكره الشرباصي.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>١٢١-<span class="c1">"المُنتقمُ"</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">دليله:</span> قوله تعالى: <span class="c3">{إِنَّا مِنَ الْمُجْرِمِينَ مُنْتَقِمُونَ}</span> . <span class="c2">(السجدة: من الآية٢٢)</span> .<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>